        <hediff>BX_SoulCraving</hediff>
        <stages>
            <li>
                <label>soul energy craving</label>
                <description>I feel an intense yearning for soul essence.</description>
                <baseMoodEffect>-10</baseMoodEffect>
            </li>
            <li>
                <label>soul energy craving</label>
                <description>I find myself irresistibly drawn to the life force of others, my desperation driving me to increasingly risky behavior in pursuit of satisfaction.</description>
